blueprint.description:
Requirements:
-Buffer that will send signal with count of items(red wire)
-Drills that will send signals about underneath resources(red wire)
-You have to manually change recource ore and intermediate product(i.e. iron ore and plate). It must be done for input signals in the right side of scheme
-All station of 1 resource must have the same name

What this CU will do:
-Control of limit of trains by buffered amout(r.bottom comb)
-Alert if mine is depleted(most of the combs are here for this)
blueprint.label: Mining station control unit(front input)
